{"tid":1116642,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"20歲出通宵街比老豆老母禁","createTime":"2019-04-20T06:44:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-20T08:20:44.000Z","uid":245958,"like":27,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"06872542761ebc8ea5b7cb4f137ae035179d291b","tid":1116642,"uid":245958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T06:44:26.000Z","msg":"有無巴絲打到廿歲都唔出得通宵街<br />\n以前中學雞1x 就話姐<br />\n老豆竟然同我講出得通宵街都係無家教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我又唔係去邊危險地方果種<br />\n連中秋想通頂玩下螢光棒都唔比同我設門禁<br />\n<br />\n到底係依家社會延遲到30先係成年標準<br />\n定係我屋企太嚴問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a22a85fc5efda858f7c5fbc3c62802a802077da","tid":1116642,"uid":82404,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T06:45:45.000Z","msg":"我10歲就出得通宵街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b583e4e2be2a609c16b9106559a93d4c0b60da52","tid":1116642,"uid":161988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T06:47:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"824c2265e1943b6316aa04385c2e20f3cf248c87","tid":1116642,"uid":245958,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6a22a85fc5efda858f7c5fbc3c62802a802077da","tid":1116642,"uid":82404,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T06:45:45.000Z","msg":"我10歲就出得通宵街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T06:48:56.000Z","msg":"係咪男仔早啲喳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過大左成10年